version_description: Well-aligned and complete chords for the whole song / intermediate version with slash chords / suggestions for playable voicings.

Elton John wrote this song for the "American Epics Sessions" in 2017. Recorded with Jack White. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TLzxivuK8OM I could not find tabs online so this is my best shot at transcribing. I wrote it in the same key as the original but I prefer to play in the key of E to skip the barre chords (play B7 instead of B.).
